summary:
Energetic project manager with a 'can do' mentality, passionate about making a difference by mobilising and motivating people, bringing them together to work and excel as a team.

- 20+ years of experience in the humanitarian sector, managing various projects with diverse, dynamic   and multidisciplinary teams;
- Hands-on and result-oriented project manager with a mix of strategic, operational, training, human resources and event management expertise; 
- Fast, creative and strategic thinker, always looking for and seizing opportunities;
- Networker with strong diplomatic skills and a high level of cultural and organisational sensitivity.
